</div>

<div style="width:26px; height:26px; float:left;">
<a href="http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http://spoonforkbacon.com/2011/12/cracked-out-rice-krispies-treats/" target="_blank"><img style="border: 0pt none;" src="http://spoonforkbacon.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/stumble.jpg" class="size-full wp-image-988 alignleft" title="stumble" border="0" alt="stumble" width="26" height="26" /></a>
</div> 

<div style="width:17px; height:26px; float:left;">
<img class="size-full wp-image-989 alignleft" title="middle_line" src="http://spoonforkbacon.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/middle_line.jpg" alt="" width="17" height="26" />
</div>

<div style="width:63px; height:26px; float:left;">
<a href="http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=http://spoonforkbacon.com/2011/12/cracked-out-rice-krispies-treats/" target="_blank">          
<img class="size-full wp-image-990 alignleft" title="twitter" src="http://spoonforkbacon.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/twitter.jpg" alt="" width="63" height="26" />
</a>
</div>

<div style="width:17px; height:26px; float:left;">
